node.text:
I couldn’t fit all of the love in this video but this just shows how many AMAZING members of the education community we have. This video is dedicated to every single one of YOU. We love you, we appreciate you and are incredibly proud of everything you are doing.

THANK YOU!!! 🤍🤍🤍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 22, 2021. May be a meme of 1 person and text that says 'Me after give clear directions to begin working and my students just sit there and stare at me: tumbl @teachertrauma Do you understand the words that are coming out of my mouth?'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Tunday Strongest Kid Marcus is the strongest kid in second grade. He used to lift 12 pounds. Now he can lift 97 pounds. How much more can he lift now? Marces ison oh tarrids'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Abby Norman @abbynormansays I quit my teaching job and now make more bartending for 15 less hours week. Also I get blamed for way way less and get told thank you way way more. No lesson plans or grading papers. Remember this when people ask about the teacher shortage.'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'Reese Witherspoon Here are my tips on how to have the perfect summer body: Reese Witherspoon 1. Have a body Reese Witherspoon That's it. That's the tip.'.
Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 21, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Me: I am a strong, intelligent, well educated woman. Also me: Wed-nes-day'.
Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'finally remember what Zoom meetings remind me of. ነ'.
Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 21, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'KNOW WHAT SPARKS THE LIGHT IN YOU. THEN USE THAT LIGHT TO ILLUMINATE THE WORLD. -OPRAH WINFREY'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'WHAT'S THE GROSSEST THING YOU'VE SEEN A KID PUT IN THEIR MOUTH IN YOUR CLASSROOM? BORED TEACHERS'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, pizza and text that says 'When lunch is provided . for Teacher Appreciation Week and you just take everything you're entitled to after the hardest year ever @studentsaywhat'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The thought of going back to life without a mask scares me... I've been mouthing "fuck off" to people for months and I'm not sure I can stop.'.
Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on July 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'sorry i'm late my alarm didn't go off because i didn't set it because i don't like coming here here'.
